channel.title: [Release] ~*~*RuneWarz Source~*~*
channel.description:
Ok I have not developed a server in about a month now, been way to inactive, so my server died. I no longer want to run it so I am releasing this source hopeing that someone can update it and run it even more.
This is Havock Base, but with way more features and updates. Some things updated that havock didnt have are...
** All bugs but sleeping bag fixed ** Combat Formula Calculated better ** Godspells if you want them ** New Maps ** Clan System ** Player Kill System ** Swamp Tar Traders For Pk Points ** Custom Items like Rune Warz Masks & Rune Warz 2hs ** Lots of new Commands ** Server way more stable --- Creds to Vrunk for the help
There is probably way more but I just dont remember. Anyways this is a great pking source, probably the best so far excluding Stork.
I am not posting the www files or sql files, if you cant figure that out you do not deserve to start a server.
Credits:Server Base - Dummis ( I think) Server Updates and Fixes - Me, Lolwut22, Kasper -- Some help from Crooks and Tosh Stability Updates - Vrunk
http://www.speedyshare.com/318266709.html
